Generalization Milestones (a/the)

Within a session:

  • a_1_Noun: Child uses “a” with only one noun type
  • the_1_Noun: Child uses “the” with only one noun type
  • a_multiple_Ns: Child uses “a” with more than one noun type
  • the_multiple_Ns: Child uses “the” with more than one noun type
  • both_1_Noun: Child uses both “a” and “the” with the same noun type
  • both_multiple_Ns: Child uses both “a” and “the” with multiple noun types
